From: Alicia Codex <alicia@schlaile.de>
Date: Sun, 29 Mar 2026 18:16:18 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] PHP 8.5: Avoid null string arguments in calendar parser

---
 .../data/PhutilCalendarAbsoluteDateTime.php   |  2 +-
 .../parser/data/PhutilCalendarDuration.php    |  2 +-
 .../data/PhutilCalendarRecurrenceRule.php     | 12 ++++----
 .../calendar/parser/ics/PhutilICSParser.php   | 30 +++++++++----------
 .../calendar/parser/ics/PhutilICSWriter.php   |  2 +-
 5 files changed, 24 insertions(+), 24 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/applications/calendar/parser/data/PhutilCalendarAbsoluteDateTime.php b/src/applications/calendar/parser/data/PhutilCalendarAbsoluteDateTime.php
index 0129e6c05b..e4e2e11a08 100644
